4
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,200
The first one is suffering.

5
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:41,800
Right now we are suffering because we are in samsara, which means reincarnation.

6
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:47,800
As long as we are reincarnating, we are under tremendous suffering.

7
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:50,400
What is the cause of our suffering?

8
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:52,800
That's the second Noble Truth.

9
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:56,800
The cause of our suffering is our afflictions.

10
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:01,900
Because we have afflictions, that's why we are reincarnating.

11
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:06,700
If we don't have afflictions, then we will be out of samsara.

12
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:10,700
So the key is to get rid of our afflictions.

13
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:12,200
How do we do that?

14
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:16,200
We need to practice the path to end suffering.

15
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,200
We call it Bodhi.

16
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:21,100
Bodhi means way to enlightenment.

17
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:24,100
Usually it's the three aspects of learning.

18
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:27,900
Precepts, concentration and wisdom.

19
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:36,300
We practice these three things that are Bodhi so we can reach cessation of suffering.

20
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:39,100
That's what we call Nirvana.

21
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:41,400
Nirvana is not death.

22
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:45,300
It means when we have no more afflictions.

23
00:01:45,300 --> 00:01:49,100
When we have no more self, no more afflictions, that is the ultimate happiness.

24
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:49,900
When we have no more self, no more afflictions, that is the ultimate happiness.

