53
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:44,300
There is no way you can be out of suffering as long as you have a self.

54
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,300
So we have to contemplate.

55
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:54,300
Feelings will always end up as suffering as long as we are in Samsara.

56
00:03:54,300 --> 00:04:00,300
Our perception and our mental formation, that is our mind.

57
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:04,300
