66
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:37,300
So the mind is impermanent.

67
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:39,300
Lastly, the consciousness.

68
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:43,300
The whole world, we call it Dharma, which means everything.

69
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,300
