72
00:04:55,300 --> 00:05:01,300
When we believe our body is clean, our feeling is happy,

73
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:07,300
our mind is permanent, our consciousness is self,

74
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:13,300
that is what we call upside-down view, false views.

75
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:18,300
So we need to contemplate on the fact that it's impure, suffering,

76
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:21,300
impermanent, and non-self.

77
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,300
So how do we do that?

78
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:27,300
First, we need to understand what is our afflictions.

79
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:30,300
Let's look at the second noble truth.

80
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:32,300
