253
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:37,300
Wants to see our true nature.

254
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:40,300
The suchness, the Buddha nature.

255
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:44,300
We need to practice these in order to get here.

256
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:48,300
We should know from all the Mahayana Buddhism

