It's already within you.

265
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:13,300
You have the Buddha nature already.

266
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:19,300
So you will realize the four virtues of nirvana

267
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:26,300
which are permanence, bliss, self and purity.

268
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:30,300
They are the opposite of the four mindfulness.

269
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:32,300
Why is that?

270
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:37,300
Because before we have the upside down views.

271
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:39,300
Right now these are the truth.

272
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:42,300
They are aligned with their suchness.

273
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:46,300
You have the Buddha nature that is permanent.

274
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:49,300
Your Buddha nature is the same.

275
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:51,300
No matter which realm you are in.

276
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:54,300
And we have full blissfulness.

277
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:56,300
Bliss is our true nature.

278
00:15:56,300 --> 00:15:58,300
We are always happy.

279
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:01,300
It's not coming from greed for worldly things.

280
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:03,300
It's from our internal happiness.

281
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:05,300
Our innate nature.

282
00:16:05,300 --> 00:16:08,300
We are supposed to be happy all the time.

283
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,300
We have the self.

284
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:14,300
It's not the self we perceive as the five aggregates.

285
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:17,300
It's already the true suchness.

286
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:19,300
Our Buddha self.

287
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:20,300
That's our higher self.

288
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:22,300
The true self.

289
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,300
Lastly,

290
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:26,300
Self is always pure.

291
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:30,300
It's perfectly pure which means no afflictions.

292
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:34,300
All our afflictions are only illusion.

293
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:36,300
They don't really exist.

294
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:41,300
You can completely be awakened out of your afflictions

295
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:44,300
in one minute, in one instant.

296
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:48,300
Because you realize who you really are.

297
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:50,300
The true suchness.

298
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:52,300
In Mahayana Buddhism,

299
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:56,300
we know samsara is nirvana.

300
00:16:56,300 --> 00:16:59,300
Affliction is bodhi.

301
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:05,300
There's no difference between samsara or nirvana.

302
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:10,300
There's no difference between affliction or bodhi.

303
00:17:10,300 --> 00:17:11,300
Why?

304
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:15,300
Because we already have the Buddha nature.

305
00:17:15,300 --> 00:17:21,300
As long as you let go of your attachment to all the worldly forms,

306
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:24,300
understand everything is only illusion,

307
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:26,300
happening in a dream,

308
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:28,300
let go of the self,

309
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:31,300
you are already your true Buddha nature.

310
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:33,300
Tragama Sutra.

311
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,300
It says,

312
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:38,300
When madness ceases, bodhi appears.

313
00:17:38,300 --> 00:17:40,300
What is the madness?

314
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:47,300
The madness is our deluded mind having these illusions.

315
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:50,300
It sees this illusional self.

316
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:55,300
And go back to our true nature.

317
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:58,300
Then the bodhi naturally appears.

318
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:01,300
You are just who you are already.

319
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:05,300
The path to enlightenment

320
00:18:05,300 --> 00:18:10,300
is to understand the truth of the world,

321
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:13,300
which is the Four Noble Truths.

322
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:15,300
So that's the class for today.

323
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:16,300
Thank you for listening.

324
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:18,300
Amitabha.

